name: Talibans on bumper cars
description:
Infinite loop video composed by all the 10 pieces in this generative art series, morphed together. What you see is fundamentally how a machine "sees" Talibans on bumper cars (aided by my vision and touch).

Each of the 10 pieces is available as single image. They are minted on my primary account hicetnunc.xyz/barabeke but you will find them in the "collection" section of this secondary account, which is going to be the home for my collaborations with AI. 

From now on, all generative art by Barabeke will be posted on this secondary account.
